| Function         | Example                | Output   | Use                                      |
| ---------------- | ---------------------- | -------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| parseInt("42")   | parseInt("42")         | 42       | Convert string input to number           |
| parseFloat()     | parseFloat("3.14")     | 3.14     | Convert decimal string to float          |
| Number("123")    | Number("123")          | 123      | General string to number conversion      |
| isNaN("abc")     | isNaN("abc")           | true     | Validate number input                    |
| toFixed(2)       | (3.14159).toFixed(2)   | "3.14"   | Format decimals (e.g., prices, currency) |
